dule unless they\'re exported or global.\n\nI have a few options:\n1. Don\'t imp
ort `ProfileModule`, instead manually add `ProfileController`, `PhotoController`
, and `ProfileService` to the testing module\n2. Make `DataSource` a global prov
ider in the test module\n3. Create a mock ProfileModule\n\nOption 1 is the simpl
est. Let me update `bdd-setup.js` to not import `ProfileModule` but instead add 
