test expectation.\n\nLet me fix these issues.\n\nFor issue 1: The swipe request 
goes to `/matching/like` which is handled by `MatchingController`. The `ProfileC
ompletionGuard` is overridden to `canActivate: () => true` in `bdd-setup.js`, so
